Summary:
1. Primary Request and Intent:
   Fix the GitLab `allowGroups` membership check to use targeted API calls instead of paginating all user groups. The current implementation in `verifyUserGroups` iterates through ALL user groups via pagination (`ListGroups`), which for users with hundreds of subgroups triggers GitLab API rate limiting and causes authentication failures. Two concrete tasks:
