   - **Core problem**: Replace `ListGroups` pagination with targeted `GetGroupByPath` calls to avoid rate limiting. For each allowed group path, call `GET /groups/:encoded_path`. A 404/403 means user is not a member; a 200 means user has access (membership implied for private groups).
